    authors: ["Emily Robinson", "Jacqueline Nolis"],
    description: "You are going to need more than technical knowledge to succeed as a data scientist.  teaches you what school leaves out, from how to land your first job to the lifecycle of a data science project, and even how to become a manager.",
    price: "$23.99",
