  %{
    authors: ["Bruce Tate", "Mike Clark", "Bob Lee", "Patrick Linskey"],
    description: "In , Bruce Tate and his co-authors continue the entertaining and engaging writing style of relating true-life adventure sport experiences to antipattern themes established in Bruce's first book, the best selling .This more advanced book explores antipatterns, or common traps, within the context of EJB technology.",
